title: ../NEW Afterparty @ SSW
presenterName: Adam Cogan, Matt Wicks & William Liebenberg
eventShortDescription:
Our .NET User Group will run live Live from SSW Newcastle! Come join us for an evening of delicious food, drinks, networking and big news in Newcastle. Just 2 blocks away from the ../NEW venue - take the opportunity to meet industry experts, make connections and explore opportunities. And we might have a surprise guest...

⚠️ Please RSVP for catering purposes and venue capacity ⚠️

Agenda

5:30pm - Welcome to /NEW afterparty with a special guest at SSW Newcastle 🍴🍷

6:00pm - Tech news with Adam Cogan

6:10pm - Special presentation with Matt Wicks

6:20pm - Special presentation with William Liebenberg



--

Join us in person from 6 pm AEST in Sydney, Melbourne and Brisbane for a watch party:

SSW Sydney – Watch party 🎦
SSW Melbourne – Watch party 🎦
SSW Brisbane – Watch party 🎦
